channel.title: Dystopia EP - By Vulture
channel.description:
It’s about time I posted this. These songs are really old, especially Revolt, so be warned, this isn’t my best work. This is a more thrash ep, and includes a thrash house track, an Arabesque house track, and a future house track. Try to guess which is which!
https://soundcloud.com/vulture-x/sets/dystopia-ep
